Login and Dashboard UI Design:

Project: Loan Tracking and Utilization Monitoring System

1. Login Screen Design:

Purpose:
Allows beneficiaries and administrators to securely access the application.

UI Components:
- Application Logo
- Project Title
- Email Input Field
- Password Input Field
- Login Button
- Register Link
- Forgot Password Link

Wireframe:

+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|            [ LOGO ]              |
|                                  |
| Loan Tracking System             |
|                                  |
| Email                            |
| [______________________]         |
|                                  |
| Password                         |
| [______________________]         |
|                                  |
|      [ Login ]                   |
|                                  |
| Forgot Password?                 |
|                                  |
| New User? Register               |
+----------------------------------+

Features:
- User Authentication
- Input Validation
- Secure Login
- Role-Based Access

2. Beneficiary Dashboard Design:

Purpose:
Provides an overview of loan utilization and quick access to system modules.

UI Components:
- User Profile Section
- Loan Summary Card
- Expense Summary Card
- Remaining Balance Card
- Navigation Menu
- Notifications Section

Wireframe:

+----------------------------------+
| Dashboard                        |
+----------------------------------+
| Welcome, User                    |
+----------------------------------+
| Total Loan       : ₹50,000       |
| Total Expense    : ₹15,000       |
| Balance Amount   : ₹35,000       |
+----------------------------------+
| [ Loan Details ]                 |
| [ Add Expense ]                  |
| [ Upload Proof ]                 |
| [ View Reports ]                 |
| [ Reminders ]                    |
+----------------------------------+

Features:
- View Loan Information
- Track Expenses
- Upload Receipts and Bills
- View Reports
- Receive Notifications

3. Admin Dashboard Design:

Purpose:
Allows administrators to monitor beneficiaries, loans, and reports.

UI Components:
- Statistics Cards
- User Management Section
- Loan Monitoring Section
- Report Generation Section
- Reminder Management Section

Wireframe:

+----------------------------------+
